headline: Stock Of The Day: AI Play Quanta Services Flashes Buy Signal After Oracle Boom
summary: Although a heavy-construction company, Quanta Services — the IBD Stock of the Day — is arguably an AI stock.  The company builds electric plants and provides other services for the power grid.  The need for artificial intelligence computations is fueling a boom in data centers, which require massive amounts of electricity.
